Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2020 09:01:36 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/gt: Move ivb GT workarounds from init_clock_gating
 to workarounds
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.7.6
Git-commit: 7237b190add0794bd95979018a23eda698f2705d

commit 7237b190add0794bd95979018a23eda698f2705d upstream.

Rescue the GT workarounds from being buried inside init_clock_gating so
that we remember to apply them after a GT reset, and that they are
included in our verification that the workarounds are applied.

